\c 10
\s Vakadzi vatorwa vanodzingwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino Ezira wakati anyengetera, uye achareurura, achichema nekuzviwisira pasi pamberi peimba yaMwari, kwakaungana kwaari kubva kwaIsraeri ungano huru-huru yevarume nevakadzi nevana; nokuti vanhu vakachema kuchema kukuru.
\p
\v 2 Zvino Shekania mwanakomana waJehieri, \add umwe\add* wevanakomana vaErami, wakapindura ndokuti kuna Ezira: Isu takatadzira Mwari wedu ndokuwana vakadzi vatorwa vendudzi dzenyika; asi ikozvino tariro iriko kwaIsraeri maererano neizvi.
\v 3 Naizvozvo zvino ngatiite sungano naMwari wedu, kuti tibvise vakadzi ava vese, nevakaberekwa navo, sezano rashe wangu, nepane vanobvunda pamurairo waMwari wedu; uye ngazviitwe zvichienderana nemurairo.
\v 4 Simukai, nokuti nyaya iri pamusoro penyu, uye isu tinemwi, simbai muite.
\v 5 Zvino Ezira wakasimuka, ndokupikisa vakuru vevapristi, neVaRevhi, neVaIsraeri vese, kuti vaite zvinoenderana neshoko iri. Ivo ndokupika.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Ezira wakasimuka kubva pamberi peimba yaMwari, ndokupinda mukamuri raJohwanani mwanakomana waEriashibhi; zvino pakusvika kwakepo, chingwa haana kudya, uye mvura haana kunwa, nokuti anochema nekuda kwechitadzo chevatapwa.
\v 7 Zvino vakaita danidziro kupfuura nepaJudha nepaJerusarema kuvana vese veutapwa kuti vaungane paJerusarema,
\v 8 uye kuti ani nani asina kusvika mumazuva matatu, zvichienderana nezano remachinda nevakuru, nhumbi dzake dzese dzichatorwa, naiye achaparadzaniswa neungano yevatapwa.
\p
\v 9 Zvino varume vese vaJudha naBhenjamini vakaungana paJerusarema mumazuva matatu; waiva mwedzi wepfumbamwe, neremakumi maviri remwedzi; vanhu vese ndokugara pachivanze cheimba yaMwari, vachibvunda nekuda kwenyaya iyi uye nekuda kwemvura yekunaya.
\v 10 Zvino Ezira mupristi wakasimuka, ndokuti kwavari: Imwi makadarika ndokuwana vakadzi vatorwa, kuwedzera kutadza kwaIsraeri.
\v 11 Naizvozvo zvino itai reururo pamberi paJehovha Mwari wemadzibaba enyu, uye muite chido chake, muzvitsaure kundudzi dzenyika nekuvakadzi vatorwa.
\v 12 Zvino ungano yese yakapindura ndokuti nenzwi guru: Semashoko enyu, saizvozvo zviri pamusoro pedu kuti tizviite.
\v 13 Asi vanhu vazhinji, uye inguva yemvura zhinji, uye hatigoni kumira kunze; uye harisi basa rezuva rimwe kana mazuva maviri, nokuti tiri vazhinji vakadarika pachinhu ichi.
\v 14 Zvino machinda edu eungano ngaamire, yese uye vese vari mumaguta edu vakawana vakadzi vatorwa ngavauye panguva dzakatarwa uye pamwe navo vakuru veguta rimwe nerimwe, nevatongi varo, kusvika tadzosa kutsamwa kunopfuta kwaMwari wedu kubva kwatiri, nekuda kwenyaya iyi.
\p
\v 15 Jonatani mwanakomana waAsaheri, naJazeya mwanakomana waTikivha vega vakapikisa chinhu ichi; uye Meshurami nemuRevhi Shabhetai vakavabatsira.
\v 16 Zvino vana veutapwa vakaita saizvozvo, Ezira mupristi, varume, misoro yemadzibaba eimba yemadzibaba avo, nevese vavo nemazita; vakatsaurwa, ndokugara pazuva rekutanga remwedzi wegumi kunzvera nyaya iyi.
\v 17 Zvino vakapedzerana nevarume vese vaiva vawana vakadzi vatorwa nezuva kusvika pazuva rekutanga remwedzi wekutanga.
\p
\v 18 Nepvanakomana vevapristi pakawanikwa vaiva vawana vakadzi vatorwa. Pavanakomana vaJeshua mwanakomana waJozadhaki nehama dzake: Maaseya, naEriezeri, naJaribhi, naGedhariya.
\v 19 Zvino vakapa ruoko rwavo kubudisa vakadzi vavo, nokuti vane mhosva, vakapa gondohwe remakwai pamhosva yavo.
\v 20 Npavanakomana vaImeri, Hanani naZebhadhia.
\v 21 Nepavanakomana vaHarimi: Maaseya, naEria, naShemaya naJehieri, naUziya.
\v 22 Nepavanakomana vaPashuri: Erioenai, Maaseya, Ishimaeri, Netaneri, Jozabhadhi, naErasha.
\v 23 NepaVaRevhi: Jozabhadhi, naShimei, naKeraya (ndiye Kerita), naPetahia, Judha, naEriezeri.
\v 24 Pavaimbiwo: Eriashibhi; nepavarindi vemikova: Sharumi, naTeremi, naUri.
\v 25 Nepana Israeri: Pavanakomana vaParoshi: Ramiya, naIziya, naMarikiya, naMiyamini, naEriazari, naMirikiya, naBhenaya.
\v 26 Nepavanakomana vaErami: Mataniya, Zekariya, naJehieri, naAbhidhi, naJeremoti, naEriya.
\v 27 Nepavanakomana vaZatu, Eriowenai, Eriashibhi, Mataniya, naJeremoti, naZabhahi, naAziza.
\v 28 Nepavanakomana vaBhebhai: Jehohanani, Hanania, Zabhai, Atirai.
\v 29 Nepavanakomana vaBhani: Meshurami, Maruki, naAdhaya, Jashubhi, naSheari, naRamoti.
\v 30 Nepavanakomana vaPahati-Moabhi: Adhina, naKerari, Bhenaya, Maaseya, Matania, Bhezareeri, naBhinui, naManase.
\v 31 Nepavanakomana vaHarimi: Eriezeri, Ishiya, Marikiya, Shemaya, Shimeoni;
\v 32 Bhenjamini, Maruki, Shemariya.
\v 33 Pavanakomana vaHashumi: Matenai, Matata, Zabhadhi, Erifereti, Jeremai, Manase, Shimei.
\v 34 Pavanakomana vaBhani: Maadhai, naAmiramu, naUweri,
\v 35 Bhenaya, Bhedheya, Keruhi;
\v 36 Vhaniya, Meremoti, Eriashibhi;
\v 37 Mataniya, naMatenai, naJaasa;
\v 38 naBhani, naBhinui, Shimei;
\v 39 naSheremiya, naNatani, naAdhaya;
\v 40 naMakinedhabhai, Shashai, Sharai;
\v 41 Azareri, naSheremiya, Shemariya;
\v 42 Sharumi, Amaria, Josefa.
\v 43 Pavanakomana vaNebho: Jeieri, Matitia, Zabhadhi, Zebhina, naJadhau, naJoweri, Bhenaya.
\v 44 Ava vese vaiva vawana vakadzi vatorwa; uye varipo pakati pavo vakadzi vakavaberekera vana.
